15:T42d,This is a single-use reload cartridge consumable for the MIRUS powered endocutter system. Internal evidence is coherent and clinically complete: 45mm cartridge length, 3.5mm staple height (blue color code standard for medium tissue), 6-row formation. The brochure description aligns with standard surgical stapler reload nomenclature. No brand conflict exists—MIRUS is clearly the system brand. However, this specific reload variant (45-35-blue) should be presented as a SKU/variant within the parent family page 'MIRUS Power Endocutter 45mm Reloads' rather than as a standalone product page. Confidence reduced to 0.85 due to: (1) missing brand field in source data, (2) no external verification available, (3) typical e-commerce practice would group reload cartridges by jaw length with color/staple height as selectable options. Review required to confirm: manufacturer verification (Meril Endo Surgery), whether other staple heights (2.0mm/green, 4.1mm/black) exist in same 45mm family, and proper page architecture decision (individual vs. grouped presentation).7:["$","div",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-[#0A0A0A] text-white","children":[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org/\",\"@type\":\"Product\",\"name\":\"POWER ENDOCUTTER RELOAD 45-35 BLUE\",\"description\":\"Blue reload cartridge for MIRUS powered endocutter with 3.5mm staple height for medium tissue applications.\",\"brand\":{\"@type\":\"Brand\",\"name\":\"Meril\"},\"category\":\"Staplers\",\"manufacturer\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Meril Endo Surgery Private Limited\"},\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"AggregateOffer\",\"offerCount\":\"1\",\"lowPrice\":\"0\",\"priceCurrency\":\"INR\",\"availability\":\"https://schema.org/InStock\"}}"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-24","children":[["$","nav",null,{"className":"flex mb-10 text-sm text-muted-foreground","aria-label":"Breadc